1. Core Indiana Data
Function	API Call
List all College Football teams	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/teams
Get Indiana Team Info	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/teams/84
Get Indiana Schedule	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/teams/84/schedule?season=2024
Get Indiana Roster	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/teams/84/roster?enable=roster,projection,stats
Get Indiana News	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/news?team=84

2. League-Wide Data (Filter Indiana in Results)
Function	API Call
Scoreboard (All Dates)	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/scoreboard?dates=20240101-20241231
Rankings	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/rankings
Season Info (Start/End Dates)	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/common/v3/sports/football/college-football/season
Events (Games)	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events?dates=2024

3. Game-Level Data
(Replace {gameId} and {eid} with Indiana’s actual game/event IDs from schedule or scoreboard results)

Function	API Call
Game Summary	https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/football/college-football/summary?event={gameId}
Box Score	https://cdn.espn.com/core/college-football/boxscore?gameId={gameId}&xhr=1
Play-by-Play	https://cdn.espn.com/core/college-football/playbyplay?gameId={gameId}&xhr=1
Core Plays	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events/{eid}/competitions/{eid}/plays?limit=300
Drives	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events/{eid}/competitions/{eid}/drives

4. Odds & Betting Data
(Replace {eid} with Indiana’s event ID and {prov_id} with sportsbook provider ID, e.g., 38 for Caesars)

Function	API Call
Odds List	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events/{eid}/competitions/{eid}/odds
Specific Provider Odds	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events/{eid}/competitions/{eid}/odds/{prov_id}
Win Probabilities	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/events/{eid}/competitions/{eid}/probabilities
Against-the-Spread	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/seasons/2024/types/2/teams/84/ats

5. Historical & Seasonal
Function	API Call
List Seasons	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/seasons?limit=100
Season Details	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/seasons/2024
Weeks in Season	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/seasons/2024/types/2/weeks
Events by Week	https://sports.core.api.espn.com/v2/sports/football/leagues/college-football/seasons/2024/types/2/weeks/{week}/events